data.description: Stunning Updated Expanded RanchRecently renovated in 2021, it is located on a peaceful dead-end street with only 1 side road - ultimate privacy. Dual driveways for ample parking. Main House: Open floor concept, kitchen boasting stainless steel appliances & butcher block countertop, skylights for added natural light, 3 spacious bedrooms, and 1 full bath. Bonus: Main bedroom with a walk-in closet. Original laundry hook-up is available in the hall closet. Secondary Space: Newly fitted kitchen, cozy living area, 1 bedroom with illuminated double closets, and 1 full bath. Extra storage space under the stairway! Storage shed conveniently positioned at the side of the house and ideally situated near shopping areas, parks, major highways, and NYC transportation. Your dream home awaits.
